title: Future of Marvel
body:
This post will focus on all different Marvel properties, movies, games, characters etc. These are just thoughts but I wanted to share them. So for starters I don’t see much more coming to Spider-Man PS4, which mean people want the next game, I don’t expect that for a while either, Insomniac has said that they want to create a little universe, I imagine that will go into play before Spider-Man 2 but they haven’t said if other studios will participate or if they’ll make them all. I would really like to see a Black Panther or Wolverine game but we’ll see what they do.

In terms of movies I had a dream last night about seeing the first ¼ of Spiderman Far From Home and it included Peter going to a party that he technically wasn’t supposed to be at but walks out for some reason and gets caught so he’s running and the building is on fire (I assume from Mysterio) He puts on his Spiderman mask behind the fountain out front and investigates, finding a new priest type character and I would assume a mutant who had ice powers, she froze the building including a lot of the people in it but it stopped the fire. The priest takes out a cross and does a ritual but there was a candle on the back of it that ignited with some kind of gas that Mysterio started this with. Peter runs but realizes he’s too late and has a trippy moment where he and the ice power girl can’t function properly and neither can anyone else. He figured out there’s a cure for it in Wakanda hence the road trip Far From Home.

I could see something like that working where Black Panther and Spiderman are connected further on considering those are Marvel’s two top characters right now. As much as I want to see the symbiote suit make it’s debut in this next movie, I don’t think it’s going to happen because of Venom being apart of Sony’s universe. I think Osborn will buy the old Avengers/Stark tower and start the Harry/Peter relations. I see Hulk getting put on a shelf because of Ruffalo’s Thor leak.  And lastly hear me out, you know how everyone tried to recreate the super soldier serum and how Obidias tried to recreate the Iron Man suit. What if Dr. Doom is introduced as a combination of those, has an arc reactor, a suit and is buffed out with what he hoped was soldier serum.
